name: Senior #12 - Pradeep
description:
Pradeep is a 61-year-old bodega owner who enjoys meditation, gossiping and drinking boba milk tea. He is funny and very friendly, but can also be self-centered and a bit lazy.

He failed his art major terribly at college and then left his hometown. He is obsessed with collecting muscle tees and classical music.

Pradeep has one child with ex-boyfriend Mateo: Sundari, aged 27.
